creator: Most Wanted Software
descriptionHtml:
With vPlan Go, you execute planning quickly and easily. See your work at home, abroad, on the road or at work. Wherever you go, you always know what needs to be done.


Everything in a clear dashboard. Choose the tasks you want to do today. You can quickly switch to other days to see what has already been done or what still needs to be done. All the information you need to do your work is available in the form of cards. Optionally, you can also see the cards of your colleagues.


A task, a work order, a project... everything can be a card. View all required information within a card. Simply adjust statuses, quickly add comments and communicate with your colleagues. Add information with checklists, custom fields, photos and more.


vPlan Go is ideal for work carried out in production companies, creative agencies, assembly and installation companies, trade companies and IT companies.


vPlan Go is available in Dutch and English. Do you need help or do you have questions? You can always schedule a demo with one of our employees. Good luck and enjoy your work.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We regularly update our app to make it even better. Update the app to the latest version to take advantage of all the new features and improvements. This release includes:

- Various bug fixes.

Do you have a question? Shout out to support@vplan.com.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New in vPlan Go. Divide tasks into sub-cards. Divide tasks with subcards. Dividing large projects makes planning tasks a lot easier. In addition, you can now immediately add activities while creating a new card.

In addition, it is now possible to add time registrations to a (new) card by pressing the plus sign at the top right. You look up the desired card and add the hours to the activity. This makes it even easier to register hours.

Features you don't want to miss, check them out in the app!
